The President has signed into law S. 665, the "Rafael Ramos and Wenjian Liu National Blue Alert Act of 2015." This act requires the Department of Justice to establish a national Blue Alert communications network that will disseminate information on the serious injury or death of a law enforcement officer in the line of duty, an officer who is missing in connection with their official duties, or an imminent and credible threat to cause harm to a law enforcement officer.